  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Password tooltip is cut off in the password confirmation screen:\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/44469717-69478e80-a628-11e8-96e5-4459dd7b66dd.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTooltip is fully visible.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTooltip is below the logo area.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Provide different passwords while creating a new account\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.25\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n* Tested on Android\r\n",
