    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Firstly, this issue can only be reproduced on the Android platform, and it seems to be linked with the following issue of react-native:\r\n[https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/6802](https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/6802)\r\n\r\nBesides the password confirmation screen shown above, I found other two screens that suffer from the same problem:\r\n\r\nSign-in:\r\n![sign-in](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38782954/44538585-5621e500-a734-11e8-949a-b18d067c6e34.png)\r\n\r\nTransaction Fee:\r\n![transaction-fee](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38782954/44538599-62a63d80-a734-11e8-83e8-32519c22baeb.png)\r\n\r\nOne possible fix with small efforts is to add top-padding to the the tooltip's parent view.\r\n\r\n- Without top-padding (today):\r\n![with-border](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38782954/44538741-d8120e00-a734-11e8-82b0-92cff460759e.png)\r\n\r\n- With top-padding (a possible fix):\r\n![possible-fix](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38782954/44538755-e2340c80-a734-11e8-9099-25ee83e960e8.png)\r\n\r\nI would like to contribute to this project, and hopefully I can start with this issue. Thanks.",
